About Us
At Norwex, we are real people, making a real impact—all around the world. Our Mission is to improve quality of life by radically reducing chemicals in our homes. We do this by creating Safe Havens in every home we touch as we help families live more sustainably and safer from the effects of harmful chemicals.
As they help others, Norwex Consultants become empowered too. Our cutting-edge products allow them to earn a difference-making income for their families. And they also appreciate adding valuable time back into their calendars by setting their own schedules. 
Whether it’s reducing chemicals, living more sustainably, or leading a team of like-minded people, it all starts with the understanding that every small, conscious choice we make makes a difference. Everything we do helps deliver on the promise for a brighter future . . . for everyone.





Makinga global impact one person at a time
Visit Our Story
















Careers
At Norwex, our Purpose is simple but powerful: The idea that working together, with integrity, trust and respect as our Core Values and improving quality of life by radically reducing chemicals in our homes as our Mission, we can improve the world around us.




Can one person change the world?At Norwex – we think they can.
Ready to get started?















